        <abstract>
            <p>All young intelligent French naturalists support CD. But the professors are afraid of being called materialists, atheists, or communists.</p> 
<p>A paper of his ["Sur l’origine paléontologique", <hi rend="italic">C. R. Hebd. Acad. Sci.</hi> 84 (1877): 534–7] met with silence, except from Bureau. If only France had become Protestant!</p> 
        </abstract>
